{"tid":1059171,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[求狠批] 美國加洲十五日行程","createTime":"2019-03-13T03:14:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T06:08:19.000Z","uid":23189,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6a33a2433878a4c4551c3cb0f23c3091b1100b98","tid":1059171,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T03:14:20.000Z","msg":"幾經辛苦，終於拎到長假放！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前一路太忙都唔係好夠時間做research去睇下啲行程順唔順，希望大家狠狠咁俾啲意見我或者介紹我有咩好地方去同好嘢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先頭六日會響Los Angelas (16/3 - 21/3)<br />\n第一日行程就hea啲用嚟教下時差，所以係去Getty Center同The Americana at Brand<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二日因為係星期日，所以上網搵到有週日市集Melrose Trading Post打算去睇下，然後下晝就去Santa Monica <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第三日朝早就去睇Hollywood Sign，然後去Griffith Observatory，咁應該拎咗成朝，下晝就係Hollywood Boulevard行下，然後去探朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第四日朝早唔知做咩好，12點book咗間餐廳叫Openaire食完就去Dessert Hill Outlet行街，聽聞好大要預一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第五日去 Universal Studio 應該都唔使再plan去其他地方？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第六日會打算去MOCA同埋去啲Art Wall 影下相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時依度係LA嘅行程，之後就會去 Los Vages <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a5b41f3538b085fc3ddef62fad2a2b868d22562","tid":1059171,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T03:30:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾經辛苦，終於拎到長假放！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前一路太忙都唔係好夠時間做research去睇下啲行程順唔順，希望大家狠狠咁俾啲意見我或者介紹我有咩好地方去同好嘢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先頭六日會響Los Angelas (16/3 - 21/3)<br />\n第一日行程就hea啲用嚟教下時差，所以係去Getty Center同The Americana at Brand<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二日因為係星期日，所以上網搵到有週日市集Melrose Trading Post打算去睇下，然後下晝就去Santa Monica <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第三日朝早就去睇Hollywood Sign，然後去Griffith Observatory，咁應該拎咗成朝，下晝就係Hollywood Boulevard行下，然後去探朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第四日朝早唔知做咩好，12點book咗間餐廳叫Openaire食完就去Dessert Hill Outlet行街，聽聞好大要預一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第五日去 Universal Studio 應該都唔使再plan去其他地方？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第六日會打算去MOCA同埋去啲Art Wall 影下相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時依度係LA嘅行程，之後就會去 <span style=\"color: red;\">Las Vegas</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"43ac83cf8ac2e68942ed85f1e92ce716329cf24a","tid":1059171,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T03:39:16.000Z","msg":"完成咗LA嘅行程之後，嚟緊要面對嘅係一整日揸車嘅旅程<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先要由LA揸去San Francisco，因為有個朋友住響果度可以放低大部份行李響佢屋企先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想睇下大家知唔知邊個時段揸落去SF好？<br />\n22/3 依日應該朝早諗到LA仲有咩未完成就做埋佢然後揸落SF，之後同個Friend短聚一陣 夜晚十點就搭飛機去LV <br />\n一落機就租車，揸車由大峽谷嘅南邊進入，去住果邊嘅酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後接住嚟就係四日半響Las Vegas<br />\n第一日經過咁長嘅揸車之旅，點都休息過夠先 check out後就去睇大峽谷，由南面揸去北面⋯之後就揸去羚羊谷﹐當晚會響羚羊谷過夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二日就係去埋睇羚羊谷嘅另一邊之後就揸返去Las Vegas<br />\n第三日同第四日唔知做咩好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，之前有諗過好唔好去埋Area 51<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依度睇下有冇巴絲幫忙諗下，如果唔係都係行嚟行去又係睇下啲店鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fafb981b806e2f026b6b196f63f3189198990aeb","tid":1059171,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T03:47:46.000Z","msg":"27/3 上午又係睇下仲有咩響LV做，然後5點就搭飛機飛返去SF搵個Friend<br />\n然後果日就等個Friend帶我唔知去邊度玩，不過佢係咁同我講SF無嘢做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以第二日又嚟一個road trip去Tahoe滑雪<br />\n滑完一日之後就返返SF，之後無乜特別plan行程，不過要去嘅地方都係Fisherman's Wharf阿，果條大橋阿，斜路阿之類？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSan Francisco係唔係真係無嘢做到咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n過幾日就飛，希望大家可以幫我睇下啲行程點樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f3556ae157ebc1489b0c7bac462e13e5f076c3a","tid":1059171,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:13:05.000Z","msg":"PISH <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d075be6923c5267a34d0ab0ebe859e5998821888","tid":1059171,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:02:19.000Z","msg":"PISH<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed420d0755922ce68ea101b9f9c18e08cf4c7b39","tid":1059171,"uid":54472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:03:23.000Z","msg":"hollywood boulevard 兜個圈望過2眼可以閃㗎啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"025a1e56ad2d50561d972f3e4f44d6aebff0d86b","tid":1059171,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed420d0755922ce68ea101b9f9c18e08cf4c7b39","tid":1059171,"uid":54472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:03:23.000Z","msg":"hollywood boulevard 兜個圈望過2眼可以閃㗎啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy"