"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:52:19.000Z","msg":"我諗上SF個段都叫...... 偏快掛<br />\n有個鬼佬揸住部波子同黑妹踩, 我係SF用Turo租左部S3同佢地一齊踩返去......<br />\n中間仲去左食In-n-out<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但返SF最好6點前啦, 北面入去條橋塞到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2857228b3d43a4082ff60ae3d87e2f2dc4ef6a1","tid":1059171,"uid":101732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:56:04.000Z","msg":"點解要咁on9 LA &gt; SF &gt; LV &gt; SF<br />\n<br />\n直接租車 由la揸去Arizona去Nevada 最後先sf 行李放車"},{"pid":"b8ca93643e5d110d490a786372e9e6d664c5515b","tid":1059171,"uid":171273,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T07:11:45.000Z","msg":"首先<br />\nLA係垃圾地方<br />\nUniversal studio無野好玩<br />\nHollywood blvd無野好睇<br />\n個天文台其實無咩特別 除左扮下lalaland打下卡<br />\n又多人又勁難泊車 其實無咩好睇<br />\nDowntown周街乞衣<br />\n唔係downtown無咩好行<br />\n又24/7塞車<br />\n<br />\nLA揸去SF 塞車既話坐係freeway成9粒鐘 中途去廁所又要出freeway再入再塞過<br />\n完全唔係駕駛樂趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果係要上去 yosemite點都去兩三日啦 <br />\n<br />\n去旅行點解要糟質自己<br />\n<br />\n去nevada不如去埋lake tahoe啦"},{"pid":"d771c2eb9ed1eac75ad398b8d0d6b3b84d3345ad","tid":1059171,"uid":171273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T07:12:56.000Z","msg":"仲有個所謂hollywood sign<br />\n佢好似因為太多人去影相 周圍d借到角度影相既位都搵野封左(呢樣唔太sure 聽返黎）"},{"pid":"8c989682511e8a29b52d2e06919a53ca0a8255c8","tid":1059171,"uid":171273,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T07:15:19.000Z","msg":"美國都係national park最靚<br />\n15日嘥幾日係LA一定後悔"},{"pid":"cbf7c1101b3f07ada47dae8583c761d2468141a6","tid":1059171,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T07:19:26.000Z","msg":"大家咁講一講，搞到我連去都唔係好想去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a51d6c1f5f09209675e517be8e9dcf922a452cc","tid":1059171,"uid":201363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T07:27:54.000Z","msg":"Yosemite 最少兩三日 如果唔係寧願唔好去"},{"pid":"e54e6318e13884e2e0fa79117e6cc7e011acc943","tid":1059171,"uid":171273,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cbf7c1101b3f07ada47dae8583c761d2468141a6","tid":1059171,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T07:19:26.000Z","msg":"大家咁講一講，搞到我連去都唔係好想去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T07:31:00.000Z","msg":"個人認為santa monica唔錯<br />\n個天文台都可以去一去 <br />\n但係用幾日係LA真係唔多值<br />\n<br />\nNational park真係好撚靚<br />\n咩山羊谷 /death valley/ yosemite /joshua tree(好似燒左)<br />\n<br />\nVegas都可以玩兩日既"},{"pid":"39de5723de8136e99bba164d8f9a54af5ac217a2","tid":1059171,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T07:32:26.000Z","msg":"當然我係因為住係LA先覺得無野好玩<br />\n觀光客角度未必會咁覺得既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5faa85f7a3111d68b7bb4ccfa263f3992628aa9","tid":1059171,"uid":28104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T07:33:14.000Z","msg":"santa monica算係必去，如果有玩過gta會feel到好正<br />\n<br />\n但weekday係LA揸車真係想死<br />\n去附近既national park仲好，death valley好多景都唔錯，joshua tree就輕鬆遊，夜晚睇星好撚正（如果冇雲）"},{"pid":"cde504eb8fce6000b985379b071b40c0f56f4f20","tid":1059171,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e54e6318e13884e2e0fa79117e6cc7e011acc943","tid":1059171,"uid":171273,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cbf7c1101b3f07ada47dae8583c761d2468141a6","tid":1059171,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T07:19:26.000Z"