" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c9d3315e6c3f78dff1624bfb6b41d03f28931ca","tid":1059171,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b54da80df99bc1d86efd47699c87dca224a4a35d","tid":1059171,"uid":107417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T08:49:46.000Z","msg":"1. 點解咁奇怪唔LA搭機過SFO算? 要開成日車, 好慘喎<br />\n2. 你既然去到羚羊峽谷，唔該你走埋去Zion National Park/Bryce Canyon至翻來都得 (但一日一個National Park)<br />\n3. Vegas附近去乜鬼Area 51丫，死亡谷啦<br />\n4. 記住留翻少少時間去參觀Nevada的妓院，嘻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T10:35:00.000Z","msg":"因為俾個SF friend水咗，原本話一齊去LV，點知佢最後去唔到，但SF飛LV嘅機票訂哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75173d5f74448e3991646b2189f4d0add8eb0f0f","tid":1059171,"uid":4709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:32:01.000Z","msg":"SF 可以去napa同yosemite<br />\n<br />\n一日antelope玩唔晒upper同lower，淨係去upper就夠，之後好似上邊咁講去埋zion仲好<br />\n同埋訂定飛睇時間穩陣，果邊剩係比原住民開旅行社帶團，唔係話好多個團，high season會爆<br />\n最好就朝早睇完食飯就上路去zion, 天黑前應該會到<br />\n<br />\n你LA行程可以壓縮少少，hollywood sign 同observery玩唔足一日，可以朝早去MOCA晏就上山<br />\n<br />\n多左日子可以去palm果邊outlet, 睇風車/Joshua tree <br />\n<br />\n落去san diego 玩下又得<br />\n睇你想輕鬆遊定密質質<br />\n<br />\n我果時係SD-&gt;palm spring-&gt;LV-&gt;death valley-&gt;UTAH-&gt;SF咁玩，不過全程渣車<br />\n<br />\nLA就....個人唔鍾意所以好少去玩，通常做野先去"},{"pid":"33f4b1717ebd3b87b47584fc890266829515b8d6","tid":1059171,"uid":120850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:33:42.000Z","msg":"我係三藩市<br />\n4月11先走"},{"pid":"60c965c08fb30c6ef90d5d073bf10bf03330eff4","tid":1059171,"uid":120850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b31e9d7a4def8165cb4d224c048b5651d414ddb","tid":1059171,"uid":161125,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43ac83cf8ac2e68942ed85f1e92ce716329cf24a","tid":1059171,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T03:39:16.000Z","msg":"完成咗LA嘅行程之後，嚟緊要面對嘅係一整日揸車嘅旅程<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先要由LA揸去San Francisco，因為有個朋友住響果度可以放低大部份行李響佢屋企先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想睇下大家知唔知邊個時段揸落去SF好？<br />\n22/3 依日應該朝早諗到LA仲有咩未完成就做埋佢然後揸落SF，之後同個Friend短聚一陣 夜晚十點就搭飛機去LV <br />\n一落機就租車，揸車由大峽谷嘅南邊進入，去住果邊嘅酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後接住嚟就係四日半響Las Vegas<br />\n第一日經過咁長嘅揸車之旅，點都休息過夠先 check out後就去睇大峽谷，由南面揸去北面⋯之後就揸去羚羊谷﹐當晚會響羚羊谷過夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二日就係去埋睇羚羊谷嘅另一邊之後就揸返去Las Vegas<br />\n第三日同第四日唔知做咩好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，之前有諗過好唔好去埋Area 51<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依度睇下有冇巴絲幫忙諗下，如果唔係都係行嚟行去又係睇下啲店鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:58:26.000Z","msg":"LA 搭飛機去 SFO 啦, 唔好揸車浪費人生啦。搭飛機仲平過你揸車!<br />\n去得SF 點解唔去YOSEMITE?<br />\nLV 有錢咪睇下SHOW 叫下外國雞囉。 記得要去下羚羊峽谷! 上羚羊峽谷無咁正。 同埋要去HORSESHOE BEND。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:36:25.000Z","msg":"我哩邊 兩個人渣車會唔會化算d"},{"pid":"50251c086cb5ab99d574c2cb99feb197e09f820c","tid":1059171,"uid":157469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:37:20.000Z","msg":"Lake Tahoe for the view and snowboarding<br />\nSan Diego for Mexican food"},{"pid":"8d2d794963146057c64b68400c173b0d3a6959e3","tid":1059171,"uid":241338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:39:28.000Z","msg":"唔好黎美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />悶到仆街"},{"pid":"52eeebc67fcf368bc386fefe821dd91a73c0313f","tid":1059171,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33f4b1717ebd3b87b47584fc890266829515b8d6","tid":1059171,"uid":120850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:33:42.000Z","msg":"我係三藩市<br />\n4月11先走"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:43:56.000Z","msg":"由依家已經係美國？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSF有咩做？"