\" /> 令我諗起達哥去美國挑黑鬼籃球"},{"pid":"b3b16af201e1a78031e5e7eb5dd2427cb7af3417","tid":1059171,"uid":70496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52eeebc67fcf368bc386fefe821dd91a73c0313f","tid":1059171,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33f4b1717ebd3b87b47584fc890266829515b8d6","tid":1059171,"uid":120850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:33:42.000Z","msg":"我係三藩市<br />\n4月11先走"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:43:56.000Z","msg":"由依家已經係美國？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSF有咩做？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T12:11:40.000Z","msg":"行下金門公園？"},{"pid":"b0d88721c2918a086841dfaaa57e5395263b4f2e","tid":1059171,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T12:20:16.000Z","msg":"好似去到美國都係睇下風景，行下公園咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我要再整理一下行程先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0042b014d9b9d3b2245888818b9a8e63843054b9","tid":1059171,"uid":120850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3b16af201e1a78031e5e7eb5dd2427cb7af3417","tid":1059171,"uid":70496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52eeebc67fcf368bc386fefe821dd91a73c0313f","tid":1059171,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33f4b1717ebd3b87b47584fc890266829515b8d6","tid":1059171,"uid":120850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:33:42.000Z","msg":"我係三藩市<br />\n4月11先走"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:43:56.000Z","msg":"由依家已經係美國？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSF有咩做？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T12:11:40.000Z","msg":"行下金門公園？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T19:32:50.000Z","msg":"行過去好遠"},{"pid":"aa054039ce7cfac1ce883a1fcbdb5a8fa9b068cb","tid":1059171,"uid":161125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"60c965c08fb30c6ef90d5d073bf10bf03330eff4","tid":1059171,"uid":120850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b31e9d7a4def8165cb4d224c048b5651d414ddb","tid":1059171,"uid":161125,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43ac83cf8ac2e68942ed85f1e92ce716329cf24a","tid":1059171,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T03:39:16.000Z","msg":"完成咗LA嘅行程之後，嚟緊要面對嘅係一整日揸車嘅旅程<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先要由LA揸去San Francisco，因為有個朋友住響果度可以放低大部份行李響佢屋企先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想睇下大家知唔知邊個時段揸落去SF好？<br />\n22/3 依日應該朝早諗到LA仲有咩未完成就做埋佢然後揸落SF，之後同個Friend短聚一陣 夜晚十點就搭飛機去LV <br />\n一落機就租車，揸車由大峽谷嘅南邊進入，去住果邊嘅酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後接住嚟就係四日半響Las Vegas<br />\n第一日經過咁長嘅揸車之旅，點都休息過夠先 check out後就去睇大峽谷，由南面揸去北面⋯之後就揸去羚羊谷﹐當晚會響羚羊谷過夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二日就係去埋睇羚羊谷嘅另一邊之後就揸返去Las Vegas<br />\n第三日同第四日唔知做咩好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，之前有諗過好唔好去埋Area 51<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依度睇下有冇巴絲幫忙諗下，如果唔係都係行嚟行去又係睇下啲店鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:58:26.000Z","msg":"LA 搭飛機去 SFO 啦, 唔好揸車浪費人生啦。搭飛機仲平過你揸車!<br />\n去得SF 點解唔去YOSEMITE?<br />\nLV 有錢咪睇下SHOW 叫下外國雞囉。 記得要去下羚羊峽谷! 上羚羊峽谷無咁正。 同埋要去HORSESHOE BEND。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:36:25.000Z","msg":"我哩邊 兩個人渣車會唔會化算d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T04:00:20.000Z","msg":"問題係時間! 搭飛機要個半鍾, 加埋你早個半鍾去到都係3個鍾。<br />\n揸車起碼6個鍾仲未計塞車 加埋假設你行I-5 又無風景睇。而行US101 有景睇, 但就起碼7個鍾, 咁你一定會落車影下相睇下景。8個鍾走唔甩啦。租車既錢, one way drop off 既錢加埋油錢。唔係平。<br />\n搭飛機加埋行李應該$100 USD 有找架啦。自己compare下囉。條數都好易計。"},{"pid":"03621bfb415709996143c18e2173a3c6d5ad146b","tid":1059171,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T04:01:50.000Z","msg":"老實講LA其實無咩地方去<br />\n不過衰在你一日唔可以去到咁多地方<br />\n因為塞車都塞死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}